United States of Me # Background # Been on a nostalgia trip preparing for this video about my first recording experience, making my album &ldquo;To My Sisters. . .&rdquo; This is one of the tracks from that record; track 8 of 9, to be exact.
A little backstory;
Surprising exactly no one, I had difficulty fitting in at school. I was the subject of a lot of rumors; I was one of the first goths in my middle school and it kind of went downhill from there.
